token_info.name: What Colour Is It?
token_info.description: The current time represented as a hexadecimal colour value. The original code has been adapted to express the piece in its purest form. Originally hosted via whatcolourisit.scn9a.org in 2015, for a brief period this was the 12,098th most visited website in the world. This is the first time the original code has been online since scn9a.org became defunct.
